body.en:
In Mind manufacturing sales platform provides the capability to maintain direct database tables. These tables can be used in the system for variety of uses cases such as in Internal Price Engine, Configuration Engine, Customizing of the system etc.

The tables can be created using application interface (i.e. from SAP) or excel upload.

In Mind has developed its own IMC Script Module which would help customers write rules and calcualtions much more easily. the module comes with:

  • IMC Script editor and built in executor.
  • The editor supports syntactic and semantic check on the script language.
  • The module serves as a basis to do programmatic chages for manufacturing customers.â€‹

To support the highly customized business process and logic needs from different customers and knowing the custom nature of these requests. In Mind has opened up its system to programatically enhance the process flow in various extension points. These extension points are groovy script enabled making them easy to write and execute in cloud environment. the extension points can also call external web services to enable cross system process needs.

In Mind now supports the complex scenario to split a quote into multiple orders. The logic to split a quote is based on a very customizable Order Splitting Scheme. The schema can have multiple steps that can use data look up from quotation and/or lookup tables.

New guided selling design focuses on usability and simplicity it offers an:

  • An attractive easy to use layout.
  • Highlights the questions and answers.
  • very easy navigation between questions and final products.
  • Full integration with UPC and related products

In Mind MSP supports material substitution based on ERP data or data created with it. Two scenarios are supported:

  • For automatic substitution, the system will automatically replace the product (if it finds a substitute) when the product is added to the quotation as a line item. â€‹
  • For manual substitution, the user is prompted to approve or reject the substitution. A separate trigger point (a button on quotation view) is also provided to trigger product substitution check at user’s will.

In Mind MSP has come up with a new access control in adition to already supported role based accessc control. 

  • In Org Unit based access control customers can choose to define the org unit hierarchy and assigns employees to these org units.
  • Based on the org unit hierarchy structure the access to quote is provided.

To stop quotations from having inactive products, old configurable products or certain other errors and to make sure the products added in the quotation are accurate and most updated one, In Mind has a new mechanism to enforce checks on quote upon its submission. Available checks includeâ€‹

  • Inactive product â€‹check
  • Configurable to classified productâ€‹ check
  • Product substitutionâ€‹ check
  • Old knowledgebase to new knowledgebaseâ€‹ check

To help sales users find the product easily, MSP is able to support  grouping products within the platform. These group-to-product relations data resides in Product Group lookup table. The system allows the users to search products by their product group in UPC.â€‹

â€‹Within each group, customer has the option to mark what the recommended products are. The recommended ones will be shown on the top of UPC with thumbs up icons. â€‹

Product bundling is a popular marketing strategy in competitive product and service markets. It allows organization to increase revenue and profit by giving customers a discount through bundling certain products.  

MSP enhances to be able to support product bundling. Each product bundle can have multiple product entries, and the product comes with related quantity too. Business admin can also define discounts and other price relevant price items on bundle or product entry level.â€‹

Once the bundle is added to the quotation, the price items on bundle level are applied to the quotation and the price items on the product entry level are applied to the items respectively.â€‹

From validation point of view the system does not allow:â€‹

  • Change of the bundle created item’s quantityâ€‹
  • If any item/s from the bundle are deleted from the quotation, the entire bundle is removed from the quote.â€‹

title.en: Customizable Layout for Sales Item Configurator

body.en:
Define Your Own Custom Layout for Sales Item Configurator

The Customizable Layout allows administrator to re-organise the product configuration layout information (Group, Sub Group, position of group, subgroup and dynamic attributes) coming from ERP/IMC model (SSC/ IMC configurable product, Classified product).

 

New UI controls for Configurator ( also includes the all new Fluid Layout View )

Select the control that you want to use per characteristic. For certain characteristics, you may want to show all options upfront instead of a dropdown. Now you can have it.

Illustration of the new controls in Configurator - 

 

By enabling Fluid Layout View, you're able to see more attributes at a glance. Each UI control's width will adapt to the length of the values.
